==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Weltanschauung
<hw>Welt"an"schau`ung</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu>pl.
<plw>Weltanschauungen</plw> <pr>(#)</pr></plu>. <ety>[G.]</ety>
<def>Lit., world view; a conception of the course of events in, and of
the purpose of, the world as a whole, forming a philosophical view or
apprehension of the universe; the general idea embodied in a
cosmology.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

